'''Vine'''是[[Twitter|Twitter]]旗下的一款免费移动应用，允许用户创建最长6秒的短片并分享到到社交网络，比如Twitter和[[Facebook|Facebook]]<ref name="Mashable Hands On">{{cite web |last= Price |first= Emily |title= Hands On With Twitter's Social Video App, Vine |url= http://mashable.com/2013/01/24/hands-on-with-vine/ |publisher= Mashable |accessdate= 2013-01-26 |archive-date= 2013-01-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130127024334/http://mashable.com/2013/01/24/hands-on-with-vine/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Baldwin |first=Roberto |url=http://www.wired.com/gadgetlab/2013/03/now-you-can-embed-6-seconds-of-vine-heaven/ |title=WIRED - Now You Can Embed 6 Seconds of Vine Heaven |publisher=wired.com |date=2013-03-29 |accessdate=2013-04-10 |archive-date=2013-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130416080953/http://www.wired.com/gadgetlab/2013/03/now-you-can-embed-6-seconds-of-vine-heaven |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Vine于2013年1月24日首先登陸[[iOS|iOS]]平台、6月3日登陸[[Android|Android]]平台<ref name="allthingsd1"/><ref name="USA first">{{cite news |title=Twitter launches video sharing service Vine |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2013/01/24/twitter-vine-video-sharing/1861625/ |accessdate=2013-01-24 |newspaper=USA Today |date=2013-01-24 |first=Brett |last=Molina |archive-date=2022-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112011515/https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2013/01/24/twitter-vine-video-sharing/1861625/ }}</ref>。

==历史==
Vine在2012年6月由唐姆·霍夫曼和罗斯·优素普夫创立。2012年10月被[[Twitter|Twitter]]收购<ref name="allthingsd1">{{cite web |last=Fried |first=Ina |url=http://allthingsd.com/20121009/twitter-buys-vine-a-video-clip-company-that-never-launched/ |title=Twitter Buys Vine, a Video Clip Company That Never Launched - Peter Kafka and Mike Isaac - Mobile |publisher=AllThingsD |date=2012-10-09 |accessdate=2013-03-15 |archive-date=2014-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925082926/http://allthingsd.com/20121009/twitter-buys-vine-a-video-clip-company-that-never-launched/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年1月24日，Vine登陸[[iOS|iOS]]平台，适用于[[iPhone|iPhone]]和[[iTouch|iTouch]]<ref name="Vine Launch Tech Crunch">{{cite web |last=Crook |first=Jordan |title=Twitter’s 6-Second Video Sharing App, Vine, Goes Live In The App Store |url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/01/24/twitters-video-sharing-app-vine-goes-live-in-the-app-store/ |publisher=Tech Crunch |accessdate=2013-01-26 |archive-date=2013-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130904203114/http://techcrunch.com/2013/01/24/twitters-video-sharing-app-vine-goes-live-in-the-app-store/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。几个月后，Vine成为市场上最受欢迎的视频分享应用<ref>{{cite web |last=Moore |first=Robert |url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/03/06/771378/ |title=TechCrunch - Vine Takes Early Command In The Mobile Video Market Over Viddy, Socialcam And Others Despite Low Adoption |publisher=techcrunch.com |date=2013-03-06 |accessdate=2013-04-10 |archive-date=2022-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122204010/https://techcrunch.com/2013/03/06/771378/ }}</ref>。2013年4月9日，Vine在[[App_Store_(iOS)|App Store]]成为当日下载次数最多的免费软件<ref>{{cite web |last=Souppouris |first=Aaron |url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/4/9/4204396/vine-number-one-us-app-store-free-apps-chart |title=The Verge - Vine is now the number one free app in the US App Store |publisher=theverge.com |date=2013-04-09 |accessdate=2013-04-10 |archive-date=2017-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170501074734/http://www.theverge.com/2013/4/9/4204396/vine-number-one-us-app-store-free-apps-chart |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年6月3日，Vine登陸Android平台。

Twitter在2016年10月27日宣布将会关闭Vine作为公司重组计划的一部分，已经上传的视频并不会被删除。<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-37788052? Twitter axes Vine video service] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-37788052 |date=20220309194732 }}.BBC.2016-10-27.[2016-10-28].</ref>

==使用及评价==

[[BBC|BBC]]用“令人目瞪口呆的”来形容Vine，并表示不仅是广告机构，而且[[定格动画|定格动画]]业也注意到了Vine的潜在价值<ref>{{cite web |last=Rohrer |first=Finlo |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-21267741 |title=BBC News - Vine: Six things people have learned about six-second video in a week |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date=2013-01-31 |accessdate=2013-03-15 |archive-date=2016-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208143634/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-21267741 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Vine也被用作新闻业。2013年2月1日，一位[[土耳其|土耳其]]记者用Vine记录[[美国驻土耳其大使馆|美国驻土耳其大使馆]]外的一次自杀爆炸袭击，这段6秒的视频记录了所有的重要细节<ref>{{cite web |last=Ungerleider |first=Neal |url=http://www.fastcompany.com/3005630/fast-feed/using-vine-cover-breaking-news |title=Using Vine To Cover Breaking News |publisher=Fast Company |date=2013-02-07 |accessdate=2013-03-15 |archive-date=2016-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160428013243/http://www.fastcompany.com/3005630/fast-feed/using-vine-cover-breaking-news }}</ref>。

Vine也被[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]用来推广[[傻朋克|傻朋克]]乐队的新专辑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pitchfork.com/news/50153-daft-punk-reveal-random-access-memories-tracklist-via-vine-video|title=Daft Punk Reveal Random Access Memories Tracklist Via Vine Video|publisher=Pitchfork|date=May 2013 accessdate=2013-05-18|access-date=2013-06-05|archive-date=2022-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122204134/https://pitchfork.com/news/50153-daft-punk-reveal-random-access-memories-tracklist-via-vine-video/}}</ref>。

在Vine发行数周後，社区内即有[[色情影片|色情影片]]出现，但是Twitter的使用条款并不禁止色情<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-1023_3-57566074-93/pornographic-video-clips-already-showing-up-on-twitters-vine/?part=rss&subj=news&tag=title |title= Pornographic video clips already showing up on Twitter's Vine |last1=Musil |first1=Steven |date= 2013-01-27 |work=CNET |publisher=CNET |accessdate=2013-01-28}}</ref>。曾经有一支色情短片被标记为编辑推荐，随后Twitter表示这是一次人为错误<ref>{{cite news | url= http://www.3news.co.nz/Twitter-accidentally-promotes-porn-clip/tabid/412/articleID/284792/Default.aspx | work= 3 News NZ | title= Twitter accidentally promotes porn clip | date= 2013-01-29 | access-date= 2013-06-05 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029191713/http://www.3news.co.nz/Twitter-accidentally-promotes-porn-clip/tabid/412/articleID/284792/Default.aspx | archive-date= 2013-10-29 | dead-url= yes }}</ref>。由于色情内容违反了苹果的使用条款，2013年2月5日，Twitter在[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]的要求下将Vine的最小使用年龄从12岁提高到17岁<ref>{{cite web |url= http://halls-of-valhalla.org/news.php?id=120 |title= Waves Resulting From Twitter Vine |last1= ynori7 |date= 2013-01-28 |publisher= Valhalla News |access-date= 2013-06-05 |archive-date= 2013-09-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060238/http://halls-of-valhalla.org/news.php?id=120 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/twitters-vine-app-store-rating-17-adds-social/story?id=18420254 |title=Twitter's Vine Changes App Store Rating to +17, Adds Social Sharing Features - ABC News |publisher=Abcnews.go.com |date=2013-02-06 |accessdate=2013-03-15 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427150904/https://abcnews.go.com/Technology/twitters-vine-app-store-rating-17-adds-social/story?id=18420254 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

